summary: There are several wolf mods that add pups but all of them use adult sounds (that I've found at least) so I made some pitch shifted/compressed variations for young and teen.
descriptionHtml:
There are several wolf mods that add pups but all of them use adult sounds (that I've found at least) so I made some pitch shifted/compressed variations for young and teen. You will need to pack them in to your own mod as I am only providing the .wav files. THIS IS FREE TO USE FOR ANY AND EVERYTHING, IT TOOK ME 5 MINUTES TO MAKE SO have a blast. Credit is cool but I'm not gonna harp on it as I may never even see where these are used. Now go modders, go and UPDATE!! 

If you think anything sounds weird, let me know and I can further alter them.
Credit: Me gosh dern it. Oh and I guess someone at bethesda's dog, probably.
author: Burningspirit5
